Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.56,0:00:08.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那什麼啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.83,0:00:12.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道是 寶珠進化成的怪物!?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.54,0:00:18.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,寄身在屍花之王 泰坦．阿爾姆上嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.54,0:00:18.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs40\pos(1145.333,970)}Titan Arum
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.05,0:00:22.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這可不妙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.43,0:00:24.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼大量的魔石
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.61,0:00:26.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不斷地被吸收
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.21,0:00:53.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎 怎麼一回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.25,0:00:56.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧 那是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.70,0:01:00.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉亞
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.18,0:01:04.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,精靈...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.67,0:01:11.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,精靈是這副外表的生物嗎!?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.87,0:01:15.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉亞 我很想妳 很想妳唷
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.90,0:01:18.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一起加入我們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.58,0:01:21.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓我把妳 吃掉吧
